        <briefdescription>
<para>Boost converter task constructor. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>name</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The name of the class</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
The constructor allocate and register a mailbox and allocate the timer to supervise the maximum activation time period. By calling macro GPIO_DT_SPEC_GET it retrieves the GPIO pin information structure gpio from devicetree and checks with call of function device_is_ready if the gpio is ready for use. The private flag device_good, indicating that hardware initialization was successful, will be set according to the return value of function device_is_ready. If initialization was not successful an error message will be printed. <linebreak/>
Flag isEnabled will be set to false, in case file BOOST_ENABLED_FILENAME exists, flag will be set to true. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
