    <briefdescription>
<para>Boost converter class derived from task base class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The boost converter class switches boost converter on and off. It provides methods to set GPIO pin P0.21 in active and inactive state to switch boost converter on and off and a timer to control the duration of boost controller activity. <bold>Message Interaction:</bold><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Receive<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Timer interrupt callback</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Boost converter task (self)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Power manager task</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Transmit<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Boost converter task (self) </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
